cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL

The paper focuses on cross-modal retrieval, which involves computer vision (CV) and information retrieval (IR) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel transfer learning approach using adversarial training, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG). Additionally, the paper uses multimedia (MM) datasets and discusses the semantic consistency of the learned representations, which could also fall under the category of natural language processing (CL).
